      "description": "Required by NIG_PIC_maxwell_RK4 external_bgfield example: PIC-BG-Field=T needs USE_SUPER_B=1 compiled in. POSTI_BUILD_SUPERB=ON sets ADD_DEFINITIONS(-DUSE_SUPER_B=1).",
      "inherits": "windows-ucrt64-mpi",
      "binaryDir": "${sourceDir}/build-maxwell-rk4-superb-mpi",
